OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a bright and chilly
OL,6,Fstart, the clouds will bubble up to
OL,7,Fgive a mixture of sunny spells and
OL,8,Fshowers, locally heavy, with the risk
OL,9,Fof hail and thunder in places, during
OL,10,Fthe afternoon. Lighter winds than
OL,11,FSunday. Feeling warmer.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FEarly evening showers fading
OL,14,Fto leave a dry night, with prolonged
OL,15,Fclear spells. Turning chilly, with a
OL,16,Ftouch of frost in prone rural spots.
OL,17,FSome isolated mist and fog patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
