OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FAnother bright and chilly
OL,6,Fstart for many, before turning
OL,7,Fincreasingly cloudy from the west,
OL,8,Fwith outbreaks of light rain and
OL,9,Fdrizzle reaching western hills during
OL,10,Fthe afternoon. Breezy and mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fwith outbreaks of rain moving east
OL,14,FWednesday, clearing overnight. Windy
OL,15,Fand mild. Sunny spells with fewer and
OL,16,Flighter showers Thursday and Friday.
OL,17,FFeeling a little warmer, with lighter
OL,18,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
